Class FilterResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.FilterResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IErpsData, Serializable

    public class FilterResult
extends ErpsData
    Contains a relevance value for a subproject. The value is compared with the threshold value to make the decision what the target subproject is to be used.
